metadata.name: Plushies Hospital
metadata.description:
ᴀʟʟ ᴀʙᴏᴜᴛ

𝒫𝓁𝓊𝓈𝒽𝒾𝑒𝓈 𝐻𝑜𝓈𝓅𝒾𝓉𝒶𝓁 | 𝒜𝓇𝓉𝓌𝑜𝓇𝓀 |

I carefully turned the doorknob as usual, while entering I can sense a faint breeze and soothing sunlight.
The dreamy ambiance in this little room gives the medical ward the appearance of being a playground, with the patient group trying to play chase seeming to be the liveliest ever.
I grab my favorite scissor out of the cupboard and begin delicately handling each plush toy one at a time.
